  "local_port": 45648,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some good IVF and Fertility clinics in Hyderabad?",
  "response": "Hyderabad is home to several well-known and highly reputed IVF and fertility clinics that offer advanced treatments and personalized care. Here are some of the top-rated clinics in the city:\n\n### 1. **KIMS Cradle IVF Centre**\n   - **Location:** Kondapur, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** Part of the renowned KIMS Hospitals group, this center is equipped with state-of-the-art technology and offers a wide range of fertility treatments, including IVF, IUI, ICSI, and surrogacy.\n   - **Special Features:** Experienced doctors, high success rates, and comprehensive care.\n\n### 2. **Genesis Fertility & Laparoscopy Center**\n   - **Location:** Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** Led by Dr. Samit Sekhar, this center is known for its personalized approach to fertility treatments and high success rates in IVF.\n   - **Special Features:** Advanced reproductive technologies, holistic care, and patient-centric services.\n\n### 3. **Ovum Hospital**\n   - **Location:** Banjara Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** Specializing in fertility and reproductive medicine, Ovum Hospital offers services like IVF, ICSI, egg donation, and surrogacy.\n   - **Special Features:** Highly experienced team, advanced lab facilities, and a focus on ethical practices.\n\n### 4. **Srushti Fertility Center**\n   - **Location:** Madhapur, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** Known for its affordable and effective fertility treatments, Srushti Fertility Center provides services such as IVF, IUI, and fertility preservation.\n   - **Special Features:** Transparent pricing, patient-friendly approach, and high success rates.\n\n### 5. **Ankura Hospital for Women & Children**\n   - **Location:** Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** Ankura Hospital offers comprehensive fertility treatments, including IVF, ICSI, and egg freezing, with a focus on women\u2019s health.\n   - **Special Features:** World-class infrastructure, experienced specialists, and a multidisciplinary approach.\n\n### 6. **Angel Fertility Services**\n   - **Location:** Banjara Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** Angel Fertility Services provides a range of fertility treatments, including IVF, donor egg programs, and surrogacy.\n   - **Special Features:** Personalized care, advanced technologies, and a compassionate team.\n\n### 7. **Nova IVF Fertility**\n   - **Location:** Banjara Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** One of the largest fertility clinic chains in India, Nova IVF offers a wide range of services, including IVF, IUI, and genetic testing.\n   - **Special Features:** Experienced doctors, cutting-edge technology, and a high success rate.\n\n### 8. **CARE IVF Centre**\n   - **Location:** Banjara Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** Part of CARE Hospitals, this center provides advanced fertility treatments, including IVF, ICSI, and infertility diagnostics.\n   - **Special Features:** Multidisciplinary team, modern facilities, and patient-focused care.\n\n### 9. **Sai Kiran Hospital**\n   - **Location:** Kukatpally, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** Known for its affordable and effective fertility treatments, Sai Kiran Hospital offers services like IVF, IUI, and surrogacy.\n   - **Special Features:** Transparent pricing, experienced doctors, and a holistic approach.\n\n### 10. **Life Care Fertility Center**\n   - **Location:** Banjara Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Overview:** A trusted name in fertility treatments, Life Care offers services such as IVF, ICSI, and fertility preservation.\n   - **Special Features:** High success rates, advanced technologies, and a patient-first approach.\n\nBefore choosing a clinic, it\u2019s advisable to research their success rates, patient reviews, and the expertise of their doctors. Schedule consultations to discuss your specific needs and ensure the clinic aligns with your expectations.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
